// ---- New builtin type (append after SIGNED_TYPE(Int128, Int128Ty)) ----
// SIGNED_TYPE(Trit, TritTy)
//
// Properties:
//   - Width: 8 bits (matches int8_t storage)
//   - Alignment: 8 bits
//   - Range: -1, 0, +1 (enforced by Sema, not bit-width)
//   - Rank: below 'short' in integer conversion rank
//   - Signedness: signed
//
// The type is integer-like for arithmetic promotion purposes,
// but Sema applies Kleene-logic constraints on operators (see
// SemaChecking additions).
//
// ---- Corresponding QualType accessor in ASTContext ----
// QualType ASTContext::TritTy;  // initialized in InitBuiltinTypes()
//
// ---- sizeof / alignof ----
// case BuiltinType::Trit: Width = 8; Align = 8; break;
